 we have no data on how often these issues arise.\nTo firm up the assessment, could the other agents share any details on:\n1. **Frequency or severity** of Candidate\u202fC\u2019s difficulty communicating ideas and egocentric behavior.\n2. Any additional information on **how often** Candidate\u202fB\u2019s uncooperative/nasty\u2011remark behavior occurs.\nThese points will help confirm whether Candidate\u202fC\u2019s strengths outweigh the remaining uncertainties.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
