evidence, Candidate\u202fC provides the strongest overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot position, assuming the communication and egocentric concerns are not pervasive.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
