armony, which is critical on long flights.\n**Therefore, I vote for Candidate\u202fC** as the best overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot position, assuming the communication\u2011related weaknesses are not pervasive.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
